### Interactive vs One-Shot

**Interactive Mode** (default):
- Claude asks questions
- You provide context as you go
- More control, slower

**One-Shot Mode** (if supported):
- Provide all context upfront
- Claude runs autonomously
- Faster, less control

### Session Management

Sessions are stored in `[sessions-dir]/`:
- Each session has unique ID
- Context and research preserved
- Can resume interrupted workflows

